<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There should be a possibility to cancel path autodiscovery from the class name, or a possibilty to specify directory separator as a function param of loadClass(). At the moment such class names as e.g. "Project_has_Manager" cannot be created, because the underscores in the class names are always replaced with the path separator.</p>

<p>See Loader.php, line:70</p>

